reviewText: I gave this video a one star because they wouldn't let me give it a zero star! This video on probability contains numerous inaccurate items. It is not well done. It may make someone feel that they are understanding probability when, in fact, it is "easy to understand" because the information is not correct. I had purchased this to use in class in case I could not be there and had a substitute. I could never use such a poor video in a class.
I do not feel this video gives enough new information for the cost of the video.
